cdata.name: BitcoinTX
cdata.desc: BitcoinTX is an attempt at reformulating Bitcoin with Proof of Stake and using the X11 algorithm. Initially there was a PoW phase. After that, it was all PoS but there was a problem in the "lucky stake" code. The original developer(s) walked away. After that, they licked their wounds, started a little "crowd-fund" for a new developer to fix the code and managed to go forward with the project!
